e later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William Erdington was born in 1140, in Warwickshire, England as the son of Henry de Erdington of Ireton and Mrs Henry de Erdington of Ireton. He had at least 3 sons with Lady Margaret De Brampton, Baroness Corbet. He died in 1190, in England, at the age of 50."},"et":{"1140–1190":"1140–1190","1136–Female":"1136–Surnud","1185–1218":"1185–1218","1187–Male":"1187–Surnud","1189–Male":"1189–Surnud","1120–1192":"1120–1192","–Female":"Surnud","1190":"1190","1187":"1187","1120":"1120","1185":"1185","1140":"1140","1192":"1192","1136":"1136","1189":"1189","about 1189":"umbes 1189","before 1140":"enne 1140","about 1187":"umbes 1187","about 1185":"umbes 1185","1218":"1218","Erdington, Warwickshire, England":"Erdington, Warwickshire, England","Europe":"Europe","Erdington, Warwickshire, England, United Kingdom":"Erdington, Warwickshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"England","Warwickshire, England":"Warwickshire, England"},"fi":{"1140–1190":"1140–1190","1136–Female":"1136–Kuollut","1185–1218":"1185–1218","1187–Male":"1187–Kuollut","1189–Male":"1189–Kuollut","1120–1192":"1120–1192","–Female":"Kuollut","1190":"1190","1187":"1187","1120":"1120","1185":"1185","1140":"1140","1192":"1192","1136":"1136","1189":"1189","about 1189":"noin 1189","before 1140":"ennen vuotta 1140","about 1187":"noin 1187","about 1185":"noin 1185","1218":"1218","Erdington, Warwickshire, England":"Erdington, Warwickshire, England","Europe":"Europe","Erdington, Warwickshire, England, United Kingdom":"Erdington, Warwickshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England":"England","Warwickshire, England":"Warwickshire, England"},"fr":{"1140–1190":"1140–1190","1136–Female":"1136–Décédée","1185–1218":"1185–1218","1187–Male":"1187–Décédé","1189–Male":"1189–Décédé","1120–1192":"1120–1192","–Female":"Décédée","1190":"1190","